	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64175835"><p>There's a lot wrong with your post.</p><p>We are the centre... and so is everything else.</p><p>The scales involved are not human.  They're the scales at which masses would no longer (according to current theory) have been able to have gravitational interactions due to the limit of c and thus should not have formed coherent structures. After the instant of the Big Bang, distance and time were things and every point had a cosmic event horizon just as is the case now.</p></div>
